org.jfree.data.general

Interface DatasetSelectionState

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CategoryDatasetSelectionState, PieDatasetSelectionState, XYDatasetSelectionState
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultCategoryDataset, DefaultHighLowDataset, DefaultKeyedValues2DDataset, DefaultKeyedValuesDataset, DefaultPieDataset, JDBCCategoryDataset, JDBCPieDataset, SimpleHistogramDataset, TimeSeriesCollection, XYSeriesCollection

    public interface DatasetSelectionState
    A base interface that is extended by XYDatasetSelectionState (and in the future CategoryDatasetSelectionState (and perhaps PieDatasetSelectionState)). This enables the DatasetAndSelection class to pair up datasets and selection state.
